title: Week 12 Recap
itunes:title: Week 12 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling – recap all of week 12 including the Thanksgiving games. The heroes break down the Seahawks win over Carolina (2:38), the Browns pulling out a win with old Coach Hue Jackson on the sidelines (21:34) and another Jacksonville loss (45:05). As always, the heroes break down the Sunday Night game to close the show (1:08:36). Are the Packers done this season?
